sentences.sContent: As a group, multiplayer fabrics have the advantage of a large void volume in the non-compressible bade structure.
sentences.sContent_eng: As a group, multiplayer fabrics have the advantage of a large void volume in the non-compressible bade structure.
sentences.sCn: 作为一个组织，多层面料的优点是无效体积大在非可压缩八德结构中。

sentences.sContent: When a brake fluid boils, gas is formed within the system that is compressible and any lever stroke available goes toward compressing the gas instead of generating brake power.
sentences.sContent_eng: When a brake fluid boils, gas is formed within the system that is compressible and any lever stroke available goes toward compressing the gas instead of generating brake power.
sentences.sCn: 当刹车油沸腾时，系统内会形成可压缩的气体，并且任何可能的刹把行程都消耗在压缩这些气体而非产生制动力上。
